STEERING DOCUMENTATION:
1. INTRO
2. RUNNING CODE
3. SUGGESTIONS
4. EXAMPLE(S)

======================================================
1. INTRO
======================================================
In this directory is are directories containg examples 
of steering files used by:

  MyCrossSection
  MyData
  MyGrid
  MyPDF


======================================================
2. RUNNING CODE
======================================================
In general, to run the code:

  ./plot MyCrossSectionSteeringFile.txt

where MyCrossSectionSteeringFile.txt contains paths to
a MyData Steering file, a MyGrid steering file, and any
option MyPDF steering files for theory convolutes.


======================================================
3. SUGGESTIONS
======================================================
Please explore these direcotires in this order:

  MyCrossSection -> MyData -> MyGrid -> MyPDF

then try the example in the home project directory


======================================================
4. EXAMPLE(S)
======================================================
Try running the code with the steering files and grid
in the home project directory.

  ./plot example/atlastest.txt

